"e":248.04,"line":70},{"w":"Reserve","s":248.04,"e":248.52,"line":70},{"w":"fallin'","s":248.52,"e":249.26,"line":70},{"w":"kid","s":249.46,"e":249.74,"line":70},{"w":"stay","s":249.74,"e":250.22,"line":70},{"w":"calm","s":250.22,"e":250.62,"line":70},{"w":"And","s":250.62,"e":250.96,"line":71},{"w":"the","s":250.96,"e":251.24,"line":71},{"w":"Lord","s":251.24,"e":251.38,"line":71},{"w":"said","s":251.38,"e":251.66,"line":71},{"w":"the","s":251.66,"e":251.96,"line":71},{"w":"stone","s":251.96,"e":252.2,"line":71},{"w":"the","s":252.28,"e":252.8,"line":71},{"w":"builders","s":252.8,"e":252.98,"line":71},{"w":"refused","s":252.98,"e":253.92,"line":71},{"w":"Become","s":253.92,"e":254.4,"line":72},{"w":"the","s":254.4,"e":254.84,"line":72},{"w":"cornerstone","s":254.84,"e":255.3,"line":72},{"w":"the","s":255.5,"e":255.84,"line":72},{"w":"kingdom","s":255.84,"e":256.08,"line":72},{"w":"infused","s":257.14,"e":257.84,"line":72},{"w":"Six-five","s":257.86,"e":258.2,"line":73},{"w":"David","s":258.22,"e":258.76,"line":73},{"w":"walkin'","s":258.76,"e":259.36,"line":73},{"w":"off","s":259.36,"e":259.68,"line":73},{"w":"the","s":259.68,"e":259.96,"line":73},{"w":"field","s":259.96,"e":260.36,"line":73},{"w":"Sling","s":260.36,"e":260.36,"line":74},{"w":"in","s":260.36,"e":261.16,"line":74},{"w":"the","s":261.16,"e":261.44,"line":74},{"w":"pocket","s":261.44,"e":262.28,"line":74},{"w":"kid","s":262.9,"e":263.44,"line":74},{"w":"done","s":263.44,"e":263.94,"line":74},{"w":"healed","s":263.94,"e":263.94,"line":74},{"w":"(Selah.)","s":263.94,"e":265.7,"line":75}],"lines":[{"s":3.96,"e":6.64,"text":"They told the kid the giant was the gospel"},{"s":6.64,"e":13.02,"text":"They printed it on paper and they called it the apostle"},{"s":15.02,"e":17.04,"text":"Six-five David steppin' to the pyramid"},{"s":17.04,"e":24.02,"text":"Sling in the right hand, scripture on the syllabus"},{"s":26.48,"e":27.98,"text":"...let it ride"},{"s":40.16,"e":43.88,"text":"They built a temple out of debt and a triangle eye"},{"s":43.92,"e":46.96,"text":"Capstone floatin', told the people not to question why"},{"s":46.96,"e":50.02,"text":"Pulled the gold out the vault, put a promise in the sky"},{"s":50.02,"e":53.24,"text":"Called it currency — but the current carry every man dry"},{"s":53.24,"e":56.84,"text":"Federal Reserve — neither federal nor reserve"},{"s":56.84,"e":60,"text":"Private printing press, public catchin' every curve"},{"s":60.78,"e":63.16,"text":"1913 the snake crawled into the law"},{"s":63.16,"e":66.4,"text":"Took the people's purse and replaced it with a maw"},{"s":66.4,"e":69.56,"text":"Inflation eat the wage like a locust eat a field"},{"s":69.56,"e":73.12,"text":"Pension turn to dust 'fore the worker get to wield"},{"s":73.12,"e":75.82,"text":"Six-five David standin' where the prophets had to kneel"},{"s":75.82,"e":78.96,"text":"Stone in the pocket — and the pocket made of steel"},{"s":79.46,"e":82.3,"text":"Goliath got a forehead — kid got a stone"},{"s":82.52,"e":85.48,"text":"Goliath got a balance sheet — kid got a home"},{"s":85.76,"e":88.64,"text":"Goliath got the printing press — kid got the truth"},{"s":89.08,"e":91.64,"text":"Goliath got the centuries — kid got the youth"},{"s":91.7,"e":94.82,"text":"Six-five David, sling in the hand"},{"s":95.2,"e":97.98,"text":"Pyramid fallin' on the promised land"},{"s":97.98,"e":101.14,"text":"Capstone tumble, eye on the floor"},{"s":101.28,"e":104.3,"text":"Holy Ghost knockin' at the central bank door"},{"s":105.04,"e":107.48,"text":"Six-five David — taller than the lie"},{"s":107.48,"e":110.64,"text":"Bigger than the giant, smaller than the sky"},{"s":110.64,"e":113.8,"text":"One stone, one shot, one breath, one psalm"},{"s":113.8,"e":117.12,"text":"Federal Reserve fallin' — kid stay calm"},{"s":117.12,"e":120.08,"text":"They watermarked the dollar with an eye that never blinks"},{"s":120.5,"e":123.26,"text":"Pyramid unfinished — that's the part nobody thinks"},{"s":123.66,"e":126.44,"text":"Cornerstone rejected by the builders of the bank"},{"s":126.44,"e":129.58,"text":"Kid pick it up, put it in the sling, let it clank"},{"s":129.64,"e":132.86,"text":"Truth is the stone, voice is the velocity"},{"s":132.86,"e":136.02,"text":"Code is the leather, faith is the ferocity"},{"s":136.02,"e":139.22,"text":"Sling whirl twice, three times for the trinity"},{"s":139.22,"e":142.4,"text":"Aim for the forehead of the soul-less infinity"},{"s":142.4,"e":145.6,"text":"Goliath laughin' — armor weigh a thousand tons"},{"s":145.6,"e":148.82,"text":"Kid travel light: psalm, stone, two lungs"},{"s":148.82,"e":151.74,"text":"Five smooth pebbles, picked from the brook"},{"s":151.74,"e":155.04,"text":"One for the giant, four for whoever else shook"},{"s":155.04,"e":156.5,"text":"(They print it... they print it...)"},{"s":156.5,"e":158.28,"text":"But the kingdom ain't for sale"},{"s":158.3,"e":159.54,"text":"(They print it... they print it...)"},{"s":159.54,"e":161.52,"text":"But the breath behind the kid don't fail"},{"s":161.52,"e":162.48,"text":"(They print it... they print it...)"},{"s":162.48,"e":164.74,"text":"Pyramid teetering, capstone fall"},{"s":164.74,"e":166.78,"text":"(They print it... they print it...)"},{"s":167.16,"e":172.36,"text":"Six-five David standin' tall"},{"s":172.52,"e":174.08,"text":"...drum kicks back in..."},{"s":174.08,"e":174.46,"text":"BOOM"},{"s":187.24,"e":189.9,"text":"Pyramid crack — concrete dust on the marble"},{"s":189.9,"e":193.08,"text":"Eye on the bill blink twice, then it start to garble"},{"s":193.7,"e":196.24,"text":"Greenback faded — value never was the paper"},{"s":196.24,"e":199.86,"text":"Value was the labor of the hands the giant taper'd"},{"s":199.86,"e":202.6,"text":"Kid step over rubble where the temple used to loom"},{"s":202.6,"e":205.8,"text":"Plant a garden in the crater, watch the cornflowers bloom"},{"s":205.8,"e":209,"text":"Mint a new currency: trust, sweat, neighbor"},{"s":209,"e":212.16,"text":"Backed by the Maker, not by some paid persuader"},{"s":213.1,"e":215.32,"text":"Six-five David ain't a king, ain't a tyrant"},{"s":215.32,"e":218.6,"text":"Just the kid with the stone tellin' giants to stop lyin'"},{"s":218.6,"e":221.74,"text":"Walk the people home, leave the pyramid in pieces"},{"s":221.74,"e":225.26,"text":"Federal Reserve dissolved — and the burden finally ceases"},{"s":225.8,"e":228.48,"text":"Six-five David, sling in the hand"},{"s":228.48,"e":231.68,"text":"Pyramid fallin' on the promised land"},{"s":231.78,"e":234.82,"text":"Capstone tumble, eye on the floor"},{"s":234.82,"e":237.86,"text":"Holy Ghost knockin' at the central bank door"},{"s":239.04,"e":241.08,"text":"Six-five David — taller than the lie"},{"s":241.08,"e":244.26,"text":"Bigger than the giant, smaller than the sky"},{"s":244.26,"e":247.42,"text":"One stone, one shot, one breath, one psalm"},{"s":247.42,"e":250.62,"text":"Federal Reserve fallin' — kid stay calm"},{"s":250.62,"e":253.92,"text":"And the Lord said the stone the builders refused"},{"s":253.92,"e":257.84,"text":"Become the cornerstone the kingdom infused"},{"s":257.86,"e":260.36,"text":"Six-five David walkin' off the field"},{"s":260.36,"e":263.94,"text":"Sling in the pocket — kid done healed"},{"s":263.94,"e":265.7,"text":"(Selah.)"}],"duration":282.52,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.297Z","stats":{"whisperWords":583,"polishedWords":582,"matched":488,"matchRate":0.838}}